opicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534104\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 02, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104yhs1665702992800.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yhs1665702992800.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yhs1665702992800.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"yhs1665702992800\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n Installing Uniface on the iSeries \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Uniface installation program and related files are provided in a self-extracting zip file, which must be extracted to an IFS share.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"yhs1665702992800__context_ess_gwl_gcc\">To install Uniface:</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step\" id=\"yhs1665702992800__li_d28778e1_d28779e1_d28780e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Satisfy all requirements for installation on the iSeries. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kwm1665702876321.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kwm1665702876321.html\" title=\"To install Uniface on iSeries, you need to be familiar with the iSeries environment and system setup. You require training equivalent to at least the IBM i system operator workshop.\">iSeries Installation Requirements</a>.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"yhs1665702992800__li_d28781e1_d28782e1_d28783e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Create a user profile for the owner of the Uniface product objects. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bmd1665702876394.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bmd1665702876394.html\" title=\"To install Uniface, you must use a user profile that has restore authority on the iSeries system.\">Create an installation user profile</a>.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"yhs1665702992800__li_d28784e1_d28785e1_d28786e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Ensure that there is a TCP/IP port available, that TCP/IP is running, and that the domain is correctly configured. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cai1665702876465.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cai1665702876465.html\" title=\"Follow the procedure to ensure a valid TCP/IP connection.\">Ensure TCP/IP Connectivity</a>.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"yhs1665702992800__li_d28787e1_d28788e1_d28789e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Extract the distribution files to an IFS share on the iSeries and restore the installer. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"faa1665702992869.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/faa1665702992869.html\" title=\"You can install Uniface in one of two ways—using a virtual optical drive, or using CL commands to restore and run the installer.\">Prepare to Install on iSeries</a>.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"yhs1665702992800__li_d28793e1_d28794e1_d28795e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Install the Uniface product. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oom1665702992943.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oom1665702992943.html\" title=\"Follow the procedure to install Uniface in an iSeries environment.\">Install Uniface on iSeries</a>.\n </span>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534104\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534104\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Installing Uniface on the iSeries Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 02, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Installing Uniface on the iSeries The Uniface installation program and related files are provided in a self-extracting zip file, which must be extracted to an IFS share. To install Uniface: Satisfy all requirements for installation on the iSeries. For more information, see iSeries Installation Requirements . Create a user profile for the owner of the Uniface product objects. For more information, see Create an installation user profile . Ensure that there is a TCP/IP port available, that TCP/IP is running, and that the domain is correctly configured. For more information, see Ensure TCP/IP Connectivity . Extract the distribution files to an IFS share on the iSeries and restore the installer. For more information, see Prepare to Install on iSeries . Install the Uniface product. For more information, see Install Uniface on iSeries . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}